articles.description: Pronounced as: Va-vish-yuh. I am currently moving my projects and blogs from old website to this one, so still under construction!
articles.contents:
About Me
I am a recent graduate from the University of Nebraska - Lincoln with
a Bachelor of Arts in Economics and Mathematics. I have previously
worked as:
Economic Research Analyst @ Bureau of Business Research.
Data Analyst Intern @ Institute of Agriculture and Natural
Resources.
Research Assistant @ Department of Economics, University of
Nebraska - Lincoln.
More
I have used R for over 3 years for research, data analysis,
visualization, and machine learning. I also have experience with Python,
SQL, Tableau, AWS, and Spark. Lately, I have been seeking Data Science
opportunities.
 Theme Inspiration: Thomas
